    <detaileddescription>
<para>Static helper that validates a <ref refid="struct_f_tryll_graph_description" kindref="compound">FTryllGraphDescription</ref> for common authoring errors.</para>
<sect1 id="struct_f_tryll_workflow_issue_1autotoc_md2_1s1"><sect2 id="struct_f_tryll_workflow_issue_1autotoc_md2">
<title>Usage</title><para>Call Validate() from:<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>A &quot;Validate Workflow&quot; toolbar button in a custom asset editor.</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Blueprint / C++ tooling scripts.</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>The future visual-graph-editor canvas overlay.</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
</sect2></sect1>
<sect1 id="struct_f_tryll_workflow_issue_1autotoc_md3_1s1"><sect2 id="struct_f_tryll_workflow_issue_1autotoc_md3">
<title>Checks performed</title><para><orderedlist>
<listitem><para>StartNode is non-empty and present in Nodes.</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>No duplicate node names.</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Each exit field (on the typed params) references a node that exists in the graph, or is empty (END).</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Orphan nodes (no incoming exit and not the start node) — reported as warnings.</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Storage file-picker fields: absolute paths and &quot;..&quot; traversal are errors; kind mismatch and virtual names (no recognized extension) are warnings. </para>
</listitem></orderedlist>
</para>
</sect2></sect1>
